reviews.text: Fabulous ambience with amazing service. Their Guacamole is a must try, curated as per your needs and requirements right in front of you. Undoubtedly one of the better ones I've had in HK.

Tacos were fantastic, especially the mango shrimp, pork and pineapple, and the fried fish.  Many of the other tacos were very similar.  You need to book in advance to have a seat on taco tuesdays (50% off all tacos). 6 tacos and a beer was the perfect amount of food.
Best Mexican restaurant in HK, hands down. Authentic amazing food. The atmosphere and drinks are also great. We will be coming back soon!

Finally, a restaurant that isn't afraid to throw some condiments! Thank you so much for a delicious and affordable meal! Although the doors could have been better designed to ward off the summer heat, still thoroughly enjoyed the experience.

The food was delicious, but the service was quite poor. Their door is weird, and the waiter standing just inside did nothing as I was trying to figure out how to get in. Finally, another person came to help me!  Very difficult to get the attention of the servers, esp. for water!

reviews.text:
五月三十號中午，天陰。

五月總跟主管的長假期叉開來，今天終於可以一起來個休閒午餐。

這家餐廳隱藏於爹核士街樓上，是真正的隱藏，因為根本不知道入口在哪裡，我們懷著探秘的心情從Eric Kayser旁轉個彎，走上一條樓梯，終於找到。

原來老闆Esdras Ochoa 是 Final Table的Taco King，在香港開了一家主打正宗墨西哥捲餅的餐廳，食材全部從洛杉磯和墨西哥空運到港，質素有保證，我們都非常期待地點菜。

作為愛酒之人，我們點了一瓶Château de Fleurie Beaujolais，色澤紅潤，充滿深色花朵及泥土香氣，果香豐厚，跟今天的菜很配。

前菜是Ceviche Gonzaga Bay 檸檬汁醃生魚肉，源自秘魯，為南美洲各個國家都有的菜品，只是作法不同。依靠青檸或檸檬汁的強烈酸度醃熟魚肉，加入洋蔥、辣椒與香草等調味料增添風味，為魚肉殺菌消毒之餘，也除腥提鮮，非常醒胃。

我們各自選了$98的 3 Tacaos Platter，可以每人自選三款Tacos，價錢相宜且賣相精緻。

先從左邊開始吃，Baja Fish 炸巴哈魚玉米卷發源於墨西哥的Ensenada 港，魚是以啤酒麵糊鮮炸的龍利魚，酥脆口感跟酸辣醬融合，惹味不油膩。

Carnitas 燉豬肉玉米卷是採用傳統的做法，把豬腳肉燉至軟嫩，加上少量乾辣椒及黏果酸漿製成的Salsa Sauce，大大增添口感層次。

最後是Mango Shrimp 芒果大蝦玉米卷，蝦子以蒜香奶油煮，新鮮芳香的芒果配合適量墨西哥沙拉跟辣醬，實在太愛這清新香甜的口味。
Fabulous ambience with amazing service. Their Guacamole is a must try, curated as per your needs and requirements right in front of you. Undoubtedly one of the better ones I've had in HK.

Tacos were fantastic, especially the mango shrimp, pork and pineapple, and the fried fish.  Many of the other tacos were very similar.  You need to book in advance to have a seat on taco tuesdays (50% off all tacos). 6 tacos and a beer was the perfect amount of food.
Best Mexican restaurant in HK, hands down. Authentic amazing food. The atmosphere and drinks are also great. We will be coming back soon!

Finally, a restaurant that isn't afraid to throw some condiments! Thank you so much for a delicious and affordable meal! Although the doors could have been better designed to ward off the summer heat, still thoroughly enjoyed the experience.
